{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "575408ef-efed-4d3d-b304-f0d3e6a51495", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/575408ef-efed-4d3d-b304-f0d3e6a51495@1.pkg/1772597697219/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597698034", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/575408ef-efed-4d3d-b304-f0d3e6a51495@1.pkg/1772597697219/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597698034"}, "identifier": "575408ef-efed-4d3d-b304-f0d3e6a51495", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查理解交友的基本原则。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：题目的主旨在于强调朋友之间要相互帮助，友谊是双向的，A选项功利性交友与材料主旨不相符合，同时功利性交友也是违背友谊本质的。因此A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：材料主旨强调友谊是双向的，需要双向付出与珍视，因此B正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：材料主旨强调双向付出，而非择友的首要要求，该选项不符合题意，故C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：在友谊中诚信是维系双方关系的基石，但材料主旨并不强调诚信，该选项不符合题意。因此D错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选B</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）交友讲智慧，下列名言警句启示我们（　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）交友讲智慧，下列名言警句启示我们（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/575408ef-efed-4d3d-b304-f0d3e6a51495@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977935276", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;以利相交，利尽则散&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;功利性交友并不违背友谊本质</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;投我以木桃，报之以琼瑶&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;友谊贵在双向付出与珍视</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;友也者，友其德也&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;择友最重要的是品德而不是利益</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;与朋友交，言而有信&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;在友谊当中诚信是关系的基石</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）交友讲智慧，下列名言警句启示我们（　　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44